data.meta_description:
3 likes, 0 comments - upso.icons on May 12, 2024: "Elsa Pataky has an uncomfortable encounter with her ex at the Met Gala

Elsa Pataky is Chris Hemsworth’s happy wife, but before meeting him she had a passionate romance with Oscar winner Adrien Brody. Everyone thought their relationship would end in marriage, but it ended up in heartbreak over a decade ago and, during the Met Gala, they met again.
